transcripts.text: We are unstoppable.  A better world is possible.  We can continue with our business as usual.
Free New Deal!  Free New Deal!  We want our politicians and politicians around the world to start recognizing the crisis that we're in and to start taking action.
Climate justice!  When do we want it?  Now!  What do we want?  Climate justice!
When do we want it?  Now!  The fossil fuel agenda is dirty.  We cannot do it anymore.  Our house is on fire.  We'll see you next time.
